&lt;p align="JUSTIFY" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;code class="western"&gt;cleiton@vm1:~/Downloads$ cd&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code class="western"&gt;/opt/arduino-1.0/ &amp;amp;&amp;amp; ls&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align="JUSTIFY" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;code class="western"&gt;arduino128x128.png arduino32x32.png arduino48x48.png&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
