&lt;p align="JUSTIFY" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;code class="western"&gt;cleiton@vm1:~/Área de trabalho$ chmod&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;code class="western"&gt;755 arduino.desktop&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
